description: This file defines the interface for the DHCP Manager SSP Message Bus component, including function declarations for message bus engagement, initialization, finalization, resource cleanup, and status checks.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_MessageBusEngage
methods.description: Engages the message bus for the component with specified ID, configuration file, and path.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Initialize
methods.description: Initializes the message bus interface with provided user data.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Finalize
methods.description: Finalizes the message bus interface, performing cleanup with provided user data.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Buscheck
methods.description: Checks the status of the message bus, using user data.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_FreeResources
methods.description: Frees resources associated with the message bus, with a specified priority and user data.
